re at 0.001 \\la\nk/{Mpc}^{-1} \\la 0.005. It will be interesting to see if this feature is\nconfirmed by future data. The reconstructed and denoised P_{in}(k) is favored\nover the scale-invariant and power-law forms at \\ga 1\\sigma.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2003 00:03:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Aug 2003 21:34:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
