vor the production\nof amorphous ice as well. We predict that a significant fraction of the ice\nformed will be amorphous.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2003 10:51:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-23"}
